node.text:
Hey Peeps, 
the date for the pre-orders is getting closer, but until then we make a small Giveaway where you can win a signed copy of the book! 

How to participate : 
⚡Like us and @livrseditions 
⚡ Comment your pet's name, or the name you would like to give your future pet 

To increase your chances: 
⚡Participate on all our networks (Twitter, Insta, Facebook), one winner per network will be drawn.
⚡tag your friends
⚡Share the post

Good luck everyone 😄
 .
.
.
#giveaway #kitten #lovingreaper #book #webcomic #bookstagram #catlife

node.text:
IT'S READY!!! The Loving Reaper Hardcover Book 🐱 @livrseditions and I have been working hard on this book for months, there's so much heart and soul in it. A collection of my comics plus a few unpublished ones. A total of 20 stories and some artworks. Pre-orderers get a surprise too ;) Also, a portion of the proceeds will go to animal shelters and associations. You can pre-order from August 15th, I'll post all the necessary links and info here soon. <3 
.
.

#lovingreaper #BOOK #webcomic #cats

node.text:
[Sequel to "Little Fish"]
A new pet to "replace" the old one can be a difficult experience. But you can't replace old friends. You can always make new friends though 🙂 But always take your time to grieve ❤
.
.
.
#webcomic #sadcomic #lovingreaper #dog #dogsofinstagram #doglife #comic
